<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <p>Parabéns, <%= current_user.name %>! Você completou o teste!</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
    <div class="progress">
      <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-success progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="<%= @personalities.agreeableness %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: <%= @personalities.agreeableness * 20 %>%">
        Independente
        <span class="sr-only"><%= @personalities.agreeableness %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="<%= @personalities.agreeableness %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="background-color: #91cf91; width: <%= 100 - (@personalities.agreeableness * 20) %>%">
        Agradável
        <span class="sr-only"><%= @personalities.agreeableness %></span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="progress">
      <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-info progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="<%= @personalities.conscientiousness %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: <%= @personalities.conscientiousness * 20 %>%">
        Bagunceiro
        <span class="sr-only"><%= @personalities.conscientiousness %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="<%= @personalities.conscientiousness %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="background-color: #9bd8eb; width: <%= 100 - (@personalities.conscientiousness * 20) %>%">
        Meticuloso
        <span class="sr-only"><%= @personalities.conscientiousness %></span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="progress">
      <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-warning progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="<%= @personalities.extraversion %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: <%= @personalities.extraversion * 20 %>%">
        Introvertido
        <span class="sr-only"><%= @personalities.extraversion %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="<%= @personalities.extraversion %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="background-color: #f6ce95; width: <%= 100 - (@personalities.extraversion * 20) %>%">
        Extrovertido
        <span class="sr-only"><%= @personalities.extraversion %></span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="progress">
      <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-danger progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="<%= @personalities.neuroticism %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: <%= @personalities.neuroticism * 20 %>%">
        Constante
        <span class="sr-only"><%= @personalities.neuroticism %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="<%= @personalities.neuroticism %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="background-color: #e7908e; width: <%= 100 - (@personalities.neuroticism * 20) %>%">
        Instável
        <span class="sr-only"><%= @personalities.neuroticism %></span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="progress">
      <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="<%= @personalities.openness %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: <%= @personalities.openness * 20 %>%">
        Conservador
        <span class="sr-only"><%= @personalities.openness %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="<%= @personalities.openness %>" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="background-color: #63a0d4; width: <%= 100 - (@personalities.openness * 20) %>%">
        Liberal
        <span class="sr-only"><%= @personalities.openness %></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p>Por favor, compartilhe esse teste no seu facebook para ajudar a minha pesquisa =)</p>
  <div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://teste-personalidade.herokuapp.com" data-layout="button_count"></div>
</div>
